  "Title": "Image Hotspot Editor",
  "Description": "A property editor for Umbraco v15+ that lets content editors place a single hotspot on an image. Stores percentage coordinates and converts them to a ready-made CSS snippet via a strongly-typed C# value object. Works inside Block List and Block Grid elements through recursive image resolution.",
